{"word":"H1641 - גָּרַר - gârar - gaw-rar' - Catch","slug":"H1641","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גָּרַר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gârar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gaw-rar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Catch"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05E8;&#x05E8; - ga&#x0302;rar</b> - <i>gaw-rar'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>drag</i> off roughly; by implication to <i>bring up</i> the cud (that is, <i>ruminate</i>); by analogy to <i>saw: - </i>catch, chew, X continuing, destroy, saw."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1620\">H1620</a>, <a href=\"#/H1621\">H1621</a>, <a href=\"#/H1625\">H1625</a>, <a href=\"#/H1626\">H1626</a>, <a href=\"#/H1642\">H1642</a>, <a href=\"#/H4050\">H4050</a>"}]}